article_id:2190,category_name:Events,title_name:The Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes and Fire Emblem: Kindred Ties Events Will Be Added to the Event Compendium!,image_path:,message:<div>The Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes and Fire Emblem: Kindred Ties events will be added to the available events in the event compendium on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1621231200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>See here for details about the event compendium.</div><div><br></div><div>■Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/76e6b95011253c53d2a5ab5627f1265b.png"></div><div>Heroes from another world are thrust into the world of Dragalia Lost! As two princes clash, a bewitching emissary launches an attack with the Imperial army. It&#39;s the power to open otherworldly gates versus dragonblood in this meeting of two realms. With Heroes, motivations, and alliances intertwined, what will become of this world?</div><div><br></div><div>You can add the adventurer Alfonse to your roster and earn rewards like weapon skins by playing this event. Each weapon skin can only be obtained once.</div><div><br></div><div>■Fire Emblem: Kindred Ties</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5477633eb9ccd9005468e098634213aa.png"></div><div>Adventurers from the world of Fire Emblem Heroes have once again arrived in Dragalia Lost! What guiding hand leads the dragonblood realm toward destruction? Is it the will of a deity? An otherworldly power? Or maybe a peace-loving soul? A time of destruction draws near, and the Heroes must rise against the will of a god who seeks to seize control over powerful souls!</div><div><br></div><div>To play this event, read the epilogue for the Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes event.</div><div><br></div><div>You can add the adventurer Sharena to your roster and earn rewards like weapon skins by playing this event. Each weapon skin can only be obtained once.</div><div><br></div><div>■Notes</div><div>・All quests added this time are solo-only quests and cannot be played in co-op.</div><div>・More events will be made available in future updates.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1620712800,update_time1620703257